Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:09.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}注意到這斜陽時早已閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:17.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}伴著傍晚的風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:25.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我們就這樣輕輕閉著雙眼
Comment: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ED「数センチメンタル」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:33.90,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(0,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}近づきそうな距離でも　わからなくなる夕暮れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:42.16,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}迷い込んでいる　迷路の　出口はどこか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.45,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}異常が日常になって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.45,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}反則だ　待て待て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.41,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}別に　どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.12,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}素直になれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:55.00,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}いつまでも　このままでいたいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:59.01,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}そんな気持ちは溶けた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:07.68,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは探してた　お揃いの心を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:15.81,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕らは交わしてた　まとまらないセリフを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:23.95,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}触れたい手の熱が　心まで届いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:32.04,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}僕は背伸びしてた　大人びてる君を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.67,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}知りたいんだ　君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}近づきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:39.84,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夢じゃ足りなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:41.80,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心が痛くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:46.14,ED-JP-12,,0,0,4,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}もっと　言葉にしたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:33.90,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(0,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}夕陽下的我們是那麼近  是那麼懵懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:42.16,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}失去了方向  找尋不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.45,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不普通的日子成了日常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.45,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}這犯規了  你先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:48.41,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}其實都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.12,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我只是無法坦誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:55.00,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}或許我想要永遠這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:59.01,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}這份感情已溶於我心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:07.68,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我們一直在尋找  那顆成對的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:15.81,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我們一直在相互訴說  那不成文的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:23.95,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}透過掌心的溫暖  直擊內心的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:32.04,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}我一直在逞強  看著像個小大人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.67,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想要更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}好想靠近一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:39.84,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}不想只是夢到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:41.80,ED-CH-12,,0,0,19,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\bord0\c&HCD6F9F&}心裡滿是糾結
